{"tid":1607422,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［國殤日應節大力推］郁黨旗，又中晒point，又唔犯法，呀～～～","createTime":"2019-09-30T22:27:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-30T23:47:03.000Z","uid":310850,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"820df584155843116cfff7c32477ebeba971b186","tid":1607422,"uid":310850,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T22:27:05.000Z","msg":"呢排見巴打巴絲攞中國共產黨黨旗嚟發夢，<strong>實在覺得好正</strong>，叉雞飯都食多兩碟，唔推唔得。<br />\n<br />\n畀中共玩咗幾十年，黨國不分係中國是常識，乜嘢公權公道都畀中共玩殘晒，所以社會信任係零，社會維繫只能靠黨中央強權高壓。全世界死最多人既獨裁政權，佢認第二冇人認第一！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n所以國殤日，殤啲乜？梗係殤佢共產黨！又中point，又唔犯法啱晒和理非，又可以教育市民大眾中國搞成咁邊個先係罪魁禍首，實在係「賀佢老母」首選恩物！點解唔大力推？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n同我認住呢支旗！大家幫手推到佢上頂！賀佢老母！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hNh6LK3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%